net.java.jddac.common.type
Class Float64J2me

java.lang.Object
  net.java.jddac.common.type.Float64
      net.java.jddac.common.type.Float64J2me

public class Float64J2me
extends Float64

A J2ME representation of a 64 bit floating point number. This implementation simply stores the value as a string and does not attempt to do any interpretation of the value.
